<br />\n其實佢老豆都已經係背後幫左佢好多<br />\n同作品嘅DIO已經正過佢多多聲<br />\n有野心有霸氣有能力<br />\n如果唔係承太朗嘅白金之星進化屈返轉頭根本已經贏左</blockquote><br />\n迪奧第一部差唔多做晒所有反派會做嘅嘢<br />\n錫jojo條女 間接整死jojo隻狗 整死自己同jojo老豆再謀佢身家 呢段已經睇得出佢幾奸<br />\n第三部佢又識得集合成班替身使者打承太郎佢哋<br />\n自己又識得用世界停時間 <br />\n最後如果唔係花京院射個鐘樓承太郎死咗都唔知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無論點睇dio都係勁過吉良吉影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6630b760bf159ad8d1f9c904843fdb4b4e70b014","tid":152163,"uid":17402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T13:58:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一定係槙島聖護</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n動漫界joker<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1afd2e05eeef9dd8e9dcef225b02dbcaab28d328","tid":152163,"uid":86587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T13:58:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>槙島聖護影響世界<br />\n衝擊整個日本法治,政府體制<br />\n吉良吉影除左食冬甩同拎女人手打J仲識做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n吉良吉影貼近日常生活，更容易代入同理解佢既心理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92cbada3047d9df432b8f7e1485b3d411e4022b6","tid":152163,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T14:01:38.000Z","msg":"荒木夾硬送啲能力比佢 <br />\n<br />\n利伸: 荒木編劇好撚差"},{"pid":"f0f9530e0867a79007e7d1a505c568dd4ef4a316","tid":152163,"uid":22465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T14:03:24.000Z","msg":"藍染先係最正？"},{"pid":"5e6dbd8b7faeb7b30d1f490121f16eaa8e8d06ee","tid":152163,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T14:07:28.00